OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain in the
OL,6,FCentral Belt will soon clear east,
OL,7,Fotherwise a dry and bright evening.
OL,8,FMostly dry overnight but some patchy
OL,9,Fmist developing with also a few
OL,10,Fshowers over Argyll.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA bright start for many,
OL,13,Fotherwise it will be largely cloudy
OL,14,Fwith some showery outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fdeveloping. The rain may turn heavy at
OL,16,Ftimes in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
